This is awkward.<p>Exhibit A - September 2025 - &quot;Help build the future&quot; - Cloudflare hires 1111 interns to &quot;help build the future&quot;
[<a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.cloudflare.com&#x2F;cloudflare-1111-intern-program&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.cloudflare.com&#x2F;cloudflare-1111-intern-program&#x2F;</a>]<p>Exhibit B - May 2026 - &quot;Building for the future&quot; - Cloudflare lays off 1100 people, about 20% of their workforce to &quot;continue building the future&quot;
[<a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.cloudflare.com&#x2F;building-for-the-future&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.cloudflare.com&#x2F;building-for-the-future&#x2F;</a>]<p>I&#x27;ll finish on this quote: &quot;The future ain&#x27;t what it used to be.&quot; — Yogi Berra
